snippet.title: "Eula: Midnight Encounter at the Tavern" Piano Cover | Genshin Impact Character Demo OST
snippet.description:
Genshin Impact - Eula Teaser 「Midnight Encounter at the Tavern」 OST Piano Performance


I played the 'Eula' demo "Midnight Encounter at the Tavern" on the piano.
She is The 5-star character, which is rerunning with the pickup in the first half of version 3.8

Because Eula did not re-run for 1 year and 7 months,
She was so forgotten by users that it was even talked about whether it was a character that did not exist at all haha
But fortunately, She finally made a comeback in the last version ahead of Fontaine!!

Mondstadt "Angel's Share" Bar OST and Eula's themes are harmonized
The atmosphere goes up and down.

Thank you for listening

---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/kkRWtkpH
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
---------------------------------------------------
Nilou's 'Dance of Sabzeruz' Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/Ab97Db-3FiU
Aranara's Theme Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/YJtCY1zp94Y
'Dori' theme Insane Piano Duet Performance : https://youtu.be/7gAj7fL8edg
Collei Demo 「Sprout in the Thicket」 Piano Performance : https://youtu.be/4_P8vIO2EXI
